Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.18,0:00:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As times change, difficult\Ncases increase in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.68,0:00:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case is a manhunt!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.59,0:00:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put out the flames of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.59,0:00:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the truth\Nin people's hearts,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.51,0:00:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cactus Flower Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.34,0:02:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Okaya Noriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping you\Ncould find the address
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.52,0:02:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of a man named\NKitagawa Tsuyoshi-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my asking,\Nbut how are you two related?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.73,0:02:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met him in early June,\Nduring a trip to Shinshu...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think much\Nof him at the time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but lately I've\Nwanted to see him again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it!\NYou've fallen in love with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.05,0:02:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a simple search.\NNo need for me here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.31,0:02:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's some tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.93,0:02:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's she so nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any clues or leads?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.19,0:02:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. His license plate number
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a quick sketch of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.20,0:03:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! He's quite\Nthe unique individual!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.12,0:03:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, just leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.75,0:03:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sketch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.55,0:03:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This'll be a cinch! I can\Nuse his license plate number
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.14,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to get his address from\Nthe transportation office!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure she really likes him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.56,0:03:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that when\Nyou draw someone's picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.52,0:03:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your feelings for\Nthat person go into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her drawing doesn't look very--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.70,0:03:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough of your lip!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go do your homework\Nand mind your own business!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}. You shouldn't\Nget in the way of--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okaya Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}, lives at--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of his work!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already saw what I needed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A handkerchief. Is it hers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.98,0:04:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.32,0:04:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see. 3-9-8...\NSumire Lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.32,0:04:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for bringing\Nme my handkerchief!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}. Want some cocoa?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.00,0:04:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a minute, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a nice apartment!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.67,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what's your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I used to work\Nat a business firm,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? How come?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.52,0:04:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got sick.\NI'm recuperating now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kerosene?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.53,0:05:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any gas heaters...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.87,0:05:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A can of mace.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dated May 19th...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.46,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now. Is a girl's\Napartment that rare for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was my boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.80,0:05:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until he dumped me a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.43,0:05:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So now I'm looking\Nfor a new boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:41.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man in the sketch\Nsure seems different, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.90,0:05:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking things might go smoother\Nwith a different type of person!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough about me.\NTell me about yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you have a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.08,0:06:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't learn much about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.92,0:06:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. I guess I'll\Nwait around for the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.76,0:06:11.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But will he really\Nfind him that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:18.06,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,One Week Later
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been\Nto the aquarium in forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.81,0:06:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither! I hope\NI can pet the dolphins!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.07,0:06:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad about the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.53,0:06:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It probably won't rain, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man's working again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Kitagawa guy moved
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without giving his new address\Nto the transportation office.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.21,0:06:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is gonna take awhile...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it was strange\Nshe hired a detective
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.68,0:06:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when she already had\Nhis license plate number...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's what this really is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why does she look so sad?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.32,0:07:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! I just remembered\NI hafta do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.32,0:07:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.86,0:07:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers and mourning clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's visiting a grave?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder whose grave it is.\NIt still looks new.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeki-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hard to believe it's been\Nsix months already...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.82,0:07:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.45,0:07:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Much better.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for everything you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, all I did was help\Nwith your rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did all the hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.09,0:08:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say we\Nhave coffee somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.38,0:08:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I need to hurry home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Then let me drive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. Thanks, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.73,0:08:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:26.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.90,0:08:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose grave is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friend's.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.20,0:08:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it was that\Nlady's boyfriend's grave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is. He was both\Nmy friend and her fiancé.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.00,0:08:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her fiancé? When did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.63,0:08:51.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamaguchi Family Grave
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Early June.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:53.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,June?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it!\NIt was the guy in the picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.14,0:08:59.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This was my boyfriend,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.39,0:09:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,until he dumped me a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko-{\i1}san {\i0}lied\Nabout being dumped
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when her boyfriend\Nwas actually dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.94,0:09:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:12.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, how did he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.78,0:09:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two were driving\Nthrough scenic Shinshu
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when they drove into a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.16,0:09:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon my asking,\Nbut how are you two related?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.96,0:09:31.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I met him in early June,\Nduring a trip to Shinshu...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.05,0:09:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she meet him when her\Nfiancé caused the accident?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever heard\Nthe name Kitagawa Tsuyoshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He drives a red sports car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A red sports car?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.94,0:09:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me! It has\Nto do with that lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.53,0:09:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}?!\NWho exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.82,0:10:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Conan Edogawa. A detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.29,0:10:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To think that the famous Detective\NMori would have an assistant like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the only\Nway to get you to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what are you investigating?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't give any details,\Nbut could you start
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by giving me the name\Nof Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s fiance?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.64,0:10:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name was Yamaguchi Tatsuo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He worked at the same\Ncompany as she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.69,0:10:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Earlier, you seemed surprised\Nwhen I mentioned a red sports car.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard her talking to\Nthe police after the accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.79,0:10:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A red sports car?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. There was a young\Ncouple in it, chasing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We tried to lose them, but then--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.63,0:10:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did find two sets of tire tracks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.47,0:11:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:02.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were just harassing us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.47,0:11:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At first they kept honking\Ntheir horn from behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.81,0:11:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and when we let them go ahead
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they swerved right in front of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuo-{\i1}san {\i0}tried to avoid them, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.65,0:11:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright. We're looking\Ninto the incident,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.57,0:11:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but even if we do catch them,\Nthey'll probably get off easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.74,0:11:26.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.29,0:11:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Things might've been different\Nhad you actually collided,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but as they are now, this would\Nbe deemed Yamaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was speeding, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.09,0:11:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember the car's\Nmodel or license plate number?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okaya-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.68,0:11:56.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she answered clearly with,\N"I don't remember."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.44,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she didn't remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It was really hard on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She couldn't describe\Nthe couple very well either,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.33,0:12:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and with no other leads, the police\Ninvestigation ended after only a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So those clues...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. His license plate number
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a quick sketch of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! He's quite\Nthe unique individual!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.80,0:12:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko-{\i1}san {\i0}remembered\Nhis plate number and his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does the fact that\Nshe didn't tell the police
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mean that she's going to\Ntake matters into her own hands?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeki-{\i1}san{\i0}! What was the rehabilitation\Nyou and Noriko-{\i1}san {\i0}talked about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the doctor in\Ncharge of her rehabilitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.47,0:12:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did she seem at the time?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.51,0:12:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She worked extremely hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.27,0:13:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What normally takes half a year,\Nshe did in three months.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.48,0:13:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.36,0:13:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No doubt about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her lust for revenge inspired\Nher to get better quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saeki-{\i1}san{\i0}! Let's go\Nsee Noriko-{\i1}san {\i0}right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.62,0:13:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.12,0:13:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to somehow change\NNoriko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.67,0:13:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before the old man\Nfinds this Kitagawa guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.84,0:13:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.92,0:13:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.17,0:13:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry! That's\Na Shakoba Cactus needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must've gotten\Nthere when I recently
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,took one to a friend's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.77,0:13:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Shakoba Cactus?\NWas it Yamaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0}'s?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He had raised cactuses\Nsince he was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took all of them\Nin after the accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.24,0:13:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but someone asked for one, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.33,0:14:02.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to share\Nthem with Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.58,0:14:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that would\Nonly remind her of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So she doesn't know I have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Shakoba Cactuses are\Nalso known as Christmas Cactuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if--!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, is your house far from here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.85,0:14:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's on the way\Nto Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}'s place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.31,0:14:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's stop by there first!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.40,0:14:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she's not home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.36,0:14:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's odd. There's no telling\Nwhen the old man will contact her,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.11,0:14:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she should be at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.57,0:14:40.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's\Nalready found the address?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mori Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're home?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you find out\Nthe guy's address already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.34,0:14:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, sure did!\NWasn't easy, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.21,0:14:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wore the\Nbottoms off of my shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.93,0:14:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it? Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:15:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just got off\Nthe phone with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.56,0:15:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the guy's already\Nliving with some chick,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.39,0:15:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I guess she's out of luck--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.77,0:15:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the address, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.19,0:15:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.44,0:15:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, before that couple gets killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.16,0:16:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.92,0:16:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.68,0:17:13.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko-{\i1}san {\i0}probably went\Nto the transportation office
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.27,0:17:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on her own to find\NKitagawa's address.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.07,0:17:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to find his new address,\Nshe hired the old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.90,0:17:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she was that intent\Non rehabilitation,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then there's probably no stopping\Nher from wanting vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.91,0:17:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is she planning\Nto get revenge, anyway?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.33,0:17:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, did Yamaguchi-{\i1}san {\i0}die instantly?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.96,0:17:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. He was still alive\Nafter he smashed into the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.09,0:17:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He burned to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.43,0:17:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burned?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.05,0:17:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The car's gasoline ignited\Nbefore he could be pulled out...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.56,0:17:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! That wasn't\Nkerosene at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was probably gasoline!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.44,0:18:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.15,0:18:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like you remember me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That accident wasn't our fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your excuses;\Nyou're both going to die now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.66,0:18:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.08,0:18:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two are human scum!\NGet ready to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to suffer\Nexactly like my boyfriend did!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:10.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the crazy one!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.14,0:19:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably the\Nonly way to calm her feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! What are you doin'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.34,0:19:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.34,0:19:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}!\NStop this foolishness!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay back! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing this won't bring\NYamaguchi-{\i1}san {\i0}back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.52,0:20:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!\NBut this is all I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do it! Light it on fire\Nand you'll be injured too!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.44,0:20:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.07,0:20:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no future now\Nthat Tatsuo-{\i1}san {\i0}is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.66,0:20:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The least I can do\Nis make these people pay...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew, I'm pooped...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Shakoba Cactus sure is pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.22,0:20:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They bloom in the winter,\Nso in some countries
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.60,0:20:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they're given as Christmas presents
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.06,0:20:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and even referred to\Nas Christmas Cactuses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Tatsuo-{\i1}san{\i0}'s\NShakoba Cactus?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.08,0:21:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I took in all of his\Ncactuses as mementos.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.77,0:21:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noriko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.14,0:21:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamaguchi-{\i1}san{\i0} may have died,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.56,0:21:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he lives on in\Neach one of these flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatsuo-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should've come!\NThe aquarium was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All three of us fed the dolphins!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Genta-{\i1}kun{\i0} slipped and fell!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.49,0:23:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The aquarium guy took\Na picture at that exact moment!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.29,0:23:47.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.46,0:23:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! Looks like fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.05,0:23:58.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, am I glad I didn't go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.89,0:24:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Abe took out an insurance\Npolicy on Negishi-{\i1}san{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.31,0:24:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,worth 500 million yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.69,0:24:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he had me\Nvouch for his alibi!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.94,0:24:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.45,0:24:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.16,0:24:24.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll smash in that\Nrotten head of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.16,0:24:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.71,0:24:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Akaoni Fire\NFestival Murder Case."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.85,0:24:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.32,0:24:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Left handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.78,0:24:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode's case is a little tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.36,0:24:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, *I've* read the comic.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.44,0:24:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
